0],"machine_ultra-sun-ultra-moon":[53,89,92,104,113,126,156,157,164,168,182,207,213,214,216,218,237,240,241,263,280,317,339,371,374,398,411,479,490,496,523,526,590],"machine_brilliant-diamond-shining-pearl":[53,70,89,91,104,113,126,156,157,164,168,182,203,207,213,214,240,241,249,263,264,280,317,339,371,374,398,411,431,490,523,526],"egg_sword-shield":[66,68,321,418,501],"tutor_sword-shield":[811]},"species":"machop","gen":"generation-i","leg":false,"myth":false,"baby":false,"eggs":["humanshape"],"flavor":[{"version":"red","text":"Loves to build its muscles. It trains in all styles of martial arts to become even stronger."},{"version":"blue","text":"Loves to build its muscles. It trains in all styles of martial arts to become even stronger."},{"version":"yellow","text":"Very powerful in spite of its small size. Its mastery of many types of martial arts makes it very tough."},{"version":"gold","text":"Always brimming with power, it passes time by lifting boulders. Doing so makes it even stronger."},{"version":"silver","text":"It loves to work out and build its muscles. It is never satisfied, even if it trains hard all day long."},{"version":"crystal","text":"It trains by lifting rocks in the mountains. It can even pick up a GRAVELER with ease."},{"version":"ruby","text":"MACHOP\u2019s muscles are special - they never get sore no matter how much they are used in exercise. This POK\u00e9MON has sufficient power to hurl a hundred adult humans."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"MACHOP exercises by hefting around a GRAVELER as if it were a barbell. There are some MACHOP that travel the world in a quest to master all kinds of martial arts."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It continually undertakes strenuous training to master all forms of martial arts. Its strength lets it easily hoist a sumo wrestler onto its shoulders."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its whole body is composed of muscles. Even though it\u2019s the size of a human child, it can hurl 100 grown-ups."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Loves to build its muscles. It trains in all styles of martial arts to become even stronger."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It hefts a GRAVELER repeatedly to strengthen its entire body. It uses every type of martial arts."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its muscles never cramp however much it trains. It lives in the mountains away from humans."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Though small in stature, it is powerful enough to easily heft and throw a number of GEODUDE at once."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Always brimming with power, it passes time by lifting boulders. Doing so makes it even stronger."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It loves to work out and build its muscles. It is never satisfied, even if it trains hard all day long."},{"version":"black","text":"Though small in stature, it is powerful enough to easily heft and throw a number of Geodude at once."},{"version":"white","text":"Though small in stature, it is powerful enough to easily heft and throw a number of Geodude at once."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Though small in stature, it is powerful enough to easily heft and throw a number of Geodude at once."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Though small in stature, it is powerful enough to easily heft and throw a number of Geodude at once."},{"version":"x","text":"It hefts a Graveler repeatedly to strengthen its entire body. It uses every type of martial arts."},{"version":"y","text":"Its whole body is composed of muscles. Even though it\u2019s the size of a human child, it can hurl 100 grown-ups."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Machop\u2019s muscles are special\u2014they never get sore no matter how much they are used in exercise. This Pok\u00e9mon has sufficient power to hurl a hundred adult humans."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Machop exercises by hefting around a Graveler as if it were a barbell. There are some Machop that travel the world in a quest to master all kinds of martial arts."},{"version":"sun","text":"It loves working out. As it gazes at its muscles, which continue to swell day by day, it becomes more and more dedicated to its training."},{"version":"moon","text":"With its superhuman strength, it\u2019s able to throw a hundred people all at the same time. Its strength comes from lifting Graveler every day."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Once this Pok\u00e9mon has gained enough confidence and muscle from training with its friends, it challenges Makuhita to a battle."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It likes food that\u2019s highly nutritious because its instincts drive it to build muscle efficiently."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Very powerful in spite of its small size. Its mastery of many types of martial arts makes it very tough."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Very powerful in spite of its small size. Its mastery of many types of martial arts makes it very tough."},{"version":"sword","text":"Its whole body is composed of muscles. Even though it\u2019s the size of a human child, it can hurl 100 grown-ups."},{"version":"shield","text":"Always brimming with power, it passes time by lifting boulders. Doing so makes it even stronger."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Though as small as a child, it has strength enough to easily throw a well-built adult. Striving to become ever stronger, Machop trains by carrying a Graveler on its shoulders."}],"evo":{"name":"machop","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"machoke","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"machamp","level":2,"min